        long getDelayMS()
        Returns:

      • setDelayMS

        void setDelayMS(long delayMS)
        Parameters:
        delayMS - the delayMS (in milliseconds) for re-delivering messages. This value is set on the AMQ_SCHEDULED_DELAY message property when posting messages. It will only work when schedulerSupport is enabled (this can be set in the web.xml of the konakart webapp).

      • setMode

        void setMode(int mode)
        Parameters:
        mode - the mode to set. Two modes are supported - Session.AUTO_ACKNOWLEDGE = 1 (the default) and Session.SESSION_TRANSACTED = 0; Session.SESSION_TRANSACTED can only be used when programming with a local MqMgr.
